{"tid":2100721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國湖北荊門市委秘書長離奇身亡","createTime":"2020-07-09T09:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T15:32:07.000Z","uid":76591,"like":154,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"2580c704430c476f18f8769a3020ee1b223f2bf6","tid":2100721,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"中國又傳官員墜樓事件，根據中國傳媒報導，今年59歲的湖北荊門市委秘書長廖明國於7月8日下午在荊門市老市委大院墜樓身亡，目前公安部門正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n根據《澎湃新聞》報導，湖北荊門市委常委、市委秘書長廖明國昨日下午墜樓，目前公安部門正在調查，也成立專案小組，調查結果仍未出爐。據《荊門日報》報導，廖明國出生於1961年，1982年加入中國共產黨後，2016年12月起擔任荊門市市委常委、市委副秘書長、辦公室主任、市委全面從嚴治黨主體責任辦公室主任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/09/2653725-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F09%2F2653725-XXL.jpg&h=c09c792b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=776700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D776700&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=35343dd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D776700&h=bbfc41ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=776700</a>"},{"pid":"98435f6d2e93f09b4f2f5a5885702cf28fcea877","tid":2100721,"uid":294,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e02105976a32b6ecbdbb5e9649d35ada1836a85","tid":2100721,"uid":47356,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"附合國情"},{"pid":"f80ad5854a2409245535cc3ad2ed45996454ba53","tid":2100721,"uid":11809,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"被抑鬱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82acc8c1f3ed19a1cd2786b338e815563f957bd1","tid":2100721,"